<br>
&quot;Focus Items will only function on summons from level 4 to 49, Staffs of Elemental Mastery will function on summons from level 49 to 60 (Not including the Decoy summons). &quot;<br>
<br>
Does this mean the Focus Items work on 49 pets as well as the Staves of Elemental Mastery? So I could use either type of Pet 'assist'?<br>
<br>
I always understood that I could not help my 49 pets with the Focus Items. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzyphyr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zyphyr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 380<br> <font color=#333333>(7/6/02 7:54:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=540.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: level 49 pet use focus or staff? </span><hr size=1> Yes, both the Temple of SolRo foci and the Staves of Elemental Mastery work on the 49 pets. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uwillansyphus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>WillanSyphus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 200<br> <font color=#333333>(7/11/02 7:14:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=540.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: level 49 pet use focus or staff? </span><hr size=1> How big of an effect do pre-50 focus items (sol ro) have on pets? <p>[54 Elementalist] <a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=90850>Willan Syphus</a> (Gnome)<br>of the House of Elder, on Tarew Marr</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uusrbinperldashw.showPublicProfile?language=EN>usrbinperl dashw</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 64<br> <font color=#333333>(7/12/02 9:44:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=540.topic&index=3>Reply</a> 